            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "🌟 **The Millennium School, Indore: Nurturing Excellence with Care** 🌟\nMy son, Samarth, has been part of The Millennium School since KGI, and each year has been a remarkable step forward in his journey. The school’s consistent support, combined with Samarth’s dedication, has played a pivotal role in shaping his character, knowledge, and skills. We’ve witnessed his confidence soar, his curiosity thrive, and his dreams take flight within the nurturing walls of The Millennium School.\n\nThe Millennium School is not just an educational institution; it's a family. As parents, we couldn't have asked for a better place for our child's growth. Thank you, Millennium Indore, for being exceptional in every way! 🌟",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
